[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0785","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0785.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0979","title":"SCO Unixware 7.0/7.0.1/7.1/7.1.1 - Privileged Process调试导致权限提升漏洞","description":"该漏洞源于SCO Unixware系统中的特权进程机制，攻击者可通过调试器（如gdb）在特权进程执行前向_init插入陷阱，进而获得root权限。该漏洞影响范围涵盖SCO Unixware多个版本，攻击者需具备本地访问权限，通过调试器向_init插入恶意陷阱代码，绕过系统权限验证机制，最终获取系统管理员权限。漏洞利用可能导致系统完全被控制，攻击者可以任意修改系统文件、安装恶意程序或进行其他破坏性操作。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0979"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-04-11","updated":"2026-07-14","remediation":"升级到SCO Unixware最新支持版本，建议使用7.2及更高版本以获取安全修复。或者应用SCO官方发布的针对此漏洞的安全补丁包。确认系统中已应用所有最新安全更新。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T04:59:27.626521880+00:00","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/869","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94530783815434&w=2"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0785.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0274","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0274.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0699","title":"Bluestone Sapphire Web 服务器会话劫持漏洞","description":"Bluestone Sapphire Web 服务器使用可轻易猜测的会话ID（Session ID）来标识用户会话，远程攻击者无需认证即可通过暴力猜测或预测会话ID的方式劫持其他用户的会话，从而获取未授权访问权限，可能导致敏感信息泄露或越权操作。该漏洞源于会话ID生成算法缺乏足够的随机性和熵。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0699"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-04-11","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"Bluestone Sapphire Web 服务器已停止维护且厂商已被收购，建议迁移至受支持的 Web 服务器（如 Apache Tomcat 或 Nginx），并在应用层实现安全的会话管理机制，包括使用强随机数生成器创建会话ID、启用 HTTPS 加密传输、设置会话超时和 HttpOnly 标志。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/623","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-1999-0699"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0274.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0264","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0264.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0695","title":"Sybase PowerDynamo 任意文件读取漏洞","description":"Sybase PowerDynamo 个人 Web 服务器存在目录遍历漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过向目标发送包含多个 ../ 序列的特制 HTTP 请求，突破路径限制读取服务器上的任意文件（如配置文件、系统文件等），导致敏感信息泄露。该漏洞利用方式简单，攻击门槛低，CVSS v2.0 评分 5.0。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0695"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"2000-04-11","updated":"2000-04-11","remediation":"立即升级 Sybase PowerDynamo 至最新补丁版本（如 3.5.2 以上），该版本已修复 `../` 路径遍历问题。如产品已停止技术支持，应停止使用 PowerDynamo Personal Web Server，迁移至受支持的 Web 服务器（如 Apache 或 IIS），并在迁移前通过 Web 应用防火墙（WAF）配置规则拦截包含 `../` 的 URL 请求作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d92a0abc5d3abac6dcdfabfef6fd71c158e0fd8b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0695.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0695","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0695.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/58eef6eedd760f280b47bfb4c94db9995b29c5a0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0695.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-8fq5-wmgh-8gpf/GHSA-8fq5-wmgh-8gpf.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0695.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_001275.txt","https://github.com/VulnerabilityHistoryProject/mega-foss/blob/4829eeb7b0101570abbc87d2a697f2c0c2f4e5c3/src/cve/graphql/trial.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/8358776d7db47304e3a87c0f78eff81411ac0e47/1999.tsv","https://github.com/Vasileios-Mavroeidis/semantic-stix-vulnerability/blob/30f07606133364b9623f401bc306c8c9cbcf9386/vulnerability/vulnerability--e7de3a3f-5597-490f-927a-ffc41edce468.owl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0264.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0525","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0525.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0790","title":"Netscape 浏览器 JavaScript 缓存信息泄露漏洞","description":"Netscape 浏览器存在信息泄露漏洞，远程攻击者可通过构造恶意网页，诱使用户访问后利用 JavaScript 脚本读取浏览器缓存中的敏感信息。该漏洞影响 Netscape Navigator 及 Communicator 系列版本，攻击者无需身份认证即可实施攻击，可能导致用户浏览历史、会话数据等隐私信息泄露。","severity":"LOW","score":2.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0790"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-04-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:03.810","remediation":"升级至 Netscape 4.5 及以上版本以修复该漏洞；临时缓解措施可在浏览器安全设置中禁用 JavaScript 执行权限。由于 Netscape 浏览器已停止维护，建议迁移至 Mozilla Firefox 等现代浏览器，避免使用已不受支持的旧版浏览器访问互联网。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://home.netscape.com/security/notes/jscachebrowsing.html"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0525.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0262","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0262.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0693","title":"多厂商 CDE ToolTalk 共享库 TT_SESSION 环境变量缓冲区溢出本地权限提升漏洞","description":"ToolTalk 共享库处理 TT_SESSION 环境变量时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。本地攻击者可向该环境变量传入超长字符串触发缓冲区溢出，覆盖进程内存空间，从而获取 root 权限。该漏洞影响 Digital UNIX 4.0、AIX 4.3.2、CDE 2.1、IRIX 6.5.14、Solaris 7.0 及 SunOS 4.1.4 等多个 Unix 系统，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。攻击者需具有本地账号方可利用，无需用户交互。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0693"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"2000-03-02T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:51.690","remediation":"建议安装各厂商当年发布的安全补丁：Sun Solaris 用户安装 Sun Security Bulletin #192 对应补丁(如 107256-xx)；IBM AIX 4.3.2 用户安装 APAR IY07617；HP-UX 用户应用 HPSBUX9909-103 补丁；SGI IRIX 6.5.14 用户安装 SGI 安全补丁；Compaq DIGITAL UNIX 4.0 用户安装对应安全修补包。如无法立即打补丁，可将 ToolTalk 相关二进制文件移除 setuid 权限作为临时缓解措施，或禁用 CDE 环境中的 ToolTalk 服务。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/192","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/641","http://www1.itrc.hp.com/service/cki/docDisplay.do?docId=HPSBUX9909-103","https://oval.cisecurity.org/repository/search/definition/oval%3Aorg.mitre.oval%3Adef%3A4374","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19501","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d92a0abc5d3abac6dcdfabfef6fd71c158e0fd8b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0693.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0693","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0693.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/58eef6eedd760f280b47bfb4c94db9995b29c5a0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0693.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-wjxh-cxm3-22mj/GHSA-wjxh-cxm3-22mj.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0693.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_152200_152300.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_3.list.dict"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0262.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0173","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0173.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0595","title":"Microsoft Windows NT/2000 页面文件信息泄露漏洞","description":"Windows NT 及 Windows 2000 操作系统在关机时未清除系统页面文件（pagefile.sys）中的残留数据，导致内存中的敏感信息（如明文密码、密钥、用户数据等）可能被写入磁盘并长期保留。本地攻击者在获取系统访问权限后可通过读取页面文件提取这些敏感信息，造成信息泄露。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 及 Windows 2000 系统，CVSS 评分 2.1，危害等级低。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0595"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"2000-01-20T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:42.143","remediation":"通过本地安全策略启用「关机：清除虚拟内存页面文件」（路径：安全设置→本地策略→安全选项），或设置注册表 HKLM\\SYSTEM\\CurrentControlSet\\Control\\Session Manager\\Memory Management\\ClearPageFileAtShutdown 为 1。建议升级至 Windows 2000 SP4 或更高版本以降低风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/216","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2765cfa5d0fc39151c354509f5ba2b7abfdb61de/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0595.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0595","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0595.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0595.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0595.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-79qg-vhxm-8q4c/GHSA-79qg-vhxm-8q4c.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x87000/86259/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_152100_152200.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0173.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1609","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1609.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0992","title":"HP VirtualVault 未授权进程访问限制绕过漏洞","description":"HP VirtualVault 操作系统存在安全绕过漏洞。在安装了 PHSS_17692 补丁的环境中，未授权或低权限的本地进程可利用 Trusted Gateway Proxy (TGP) 组件绕过系统的访问控制限制，从而获取未授权的资源访问权限。该漏洞影响 HP VirtualVault 操作系统相关版本，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。厂商已发布补丁修复此问题。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0992"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-01-18T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:28.707","remediation":"立即安装 HP 安全公告 HPSBUX9912-107 中指定的补丁（PHSS_18263 或更新版本），该补丁修复了 Trusted Gateway Proxy (TGP) 的访问控制绕过问题。在无法安装补丁的情况下，限制非授权用户对 TGP 服务的本地访问权限，审查并收紧 TGP 配置中的访问控制规则。由于 HP VirtualVault VVOS 已停止技术支持，建议迁移至受支持的安全操作系统平台。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www1.itrc.hp.com/service/cki/docDisplay.do?docId=HPSBUX9912-107","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/c8abbfc77cc703e2fd85623576b0f07a0c8427eb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0992.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0992","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/ce91429859b5110820b1d31a41b0b1a3c67d9603/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0992.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0992.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/24ebb1752fdaa57c8d421b21085e47d359e1300e/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0992.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0992.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87941/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--7e38d2e2-f104-4783-aa45-431b0eece3d7.json","https://github.com/Yuning-J/VulnerabilityClassifier/blob/c0f06c21b73c26b5ee2b75c21a498eb04eada4b5/threatPrediction/cveIDThreatType/cve_idbypass"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1609.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0839","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0839.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1002","title":"Netscape Navigator 邮件密码弱加密存储漏洞","description":"Netscape Navigator 浏览器在存储用户邮件密码时采用弱加密算法，导致本地攻击者能够通过分析加密数据恢复明文密码。该漏洞存在于密码存储机制中，攻击者需具备本地系统访问权限，利用弱加密算法的可逆特性即可获取用户凭证信息，可能导致邮箱账户被非法访问。受影响版本包括 Netscape Navigator 全版本。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1002"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-01-12T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:29.997","remediation":"立即停止使用 Netscape Navigator 内置邮件客户端收发邮件，迁移至 Mozilla Firefox、Google Chrome 等现代浏览器或 Thunderbird 等独立邮件客户端访问邮件服务。如暂无法迁移，在 Netscape 首选项中关闭密码记忆功能，每次手动输入邮箱密码，避免凭据持久化存储于本地弱加密文件中。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94536309217214&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94570673523998&w=2","http://www.rstcorp.com/news/bad-crypto.html","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/b78238ce198ba9bb84cf32286dd81a9973f793b6/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1002.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1002","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/ce91429859b5110820b1d31a41b0b1a3c67d9603/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1002.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1002.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/24ebb1752fdaa57c8d421b21085e47d359e1300e/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1002.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-wf2x-w2q8-7723/GHSA-wf2x-w2q8-7723.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1002.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_152000_152100.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--d48d045b-59cc-4474-90a9-e6ede9ca2247.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0839.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1198","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1198.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0894","title":"Red Hat Linux screen 程序本地终端写入漏洞","description":"Red Hat Linux 的 screen 终端复用程序未使用 Unix98 伪终端（ptys），导致其创建的终端会话缺乏必要的权限隔离机制。本地攻击者可通过向其他用户使用的 screen 终端写入数据，实现会话劫持或任意命令注入。该漏洞影响 Red Hat Linux 多个版本，利用前提是攻击者拥有本地系统账户，攻击复杂度低，危害等级为高危。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0894"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-01-04T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:16.680","remediation":"升级 Red Hat Linux 至 6.2 及以上版本（默认启用 Unix98 ptys），或单独升级 screen 程序至 3.07.06 及以上版本。如无法升级，在 screen 配置文件中添加 `defunix98 on` 启用 Unix98 pty 支持，并限制本地非信任用户登录系统以降低攻击面。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0894"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1198.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1106","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1106.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0876","title":"Microsoft Internet Explorer 4.0 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Internet Explorer 4.0 在处理 EMBED 标签时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。远程攻击者可构造包含超长 EMBED 标签属性的恶意 HTML 页面，当用户使用 IE 4.0 访问该页面时触发缓冲区溢出，导致攻击者可在当前用户上下文中执行任意代码，完全控制受影响系统。该漏洞影响 Windows 平台上使用 IE 4.0 的所有版本。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0876"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-01-04T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:14.490","remediation":"立即升级 Internet Explorer 至 4.01 Service Pack 2 及以上版本，该版本修复了 EMBED 标签解析时的缓冲区溢出漏洞。对于当前仍在使用旧版 IE 的环境，建议升级至受支持的现代浏览器（如 Microsoft Edge），并禁用已停止维护的 IE 浏览器中 ActiveX 及 EMBED 标签的调用权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ185959","http://support.microsoft.com/support/kb/articles/q176/6/97.asp"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1106.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0350","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0350.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0735","title":"KDE K-Mail 符号链接攻击本地权限提升漏洞","description":"KDE K-Mail 在处理临时用户目录时存在符号链接（symlink）攻击漏洞。本地攻击者可通过在临时目录中创建恶意的符号链接，诱导 K-Mail 以高权限向攻击者控制的位置写入文件，从而实现权限提升。该漏洞影响 KDE 1.1/1.1.2、Caldera kdenetwork 1.1.1-1、Caldera OpenLinux 1.3/2.2 及 RedHat Linux 6.0 等版本，CVSS 评分 4.6，危害等级中危。攻击者需拥有本地系统访问权限方可利用。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0735"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-01-04T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:56.883","remediation":"升级 KDE 至 2.0 及以上版本（该版本重构了临时文件处理机制，采用 mkstemp 代替可预测路径）；对应发行版适用：RedHat Linux 升级至 6.0 以上 errata 内核/kdebase 包，Caldera OpenLinux 升级至 2.3 以上。临时缓解措施：为邮件用户设置私有临时目录环境变量（如 TMPDIR=/tmp/kmail-$USER）并限制目录权限为 0700。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.redhat.com/support/errata/RHSA1999015_01.html","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/300","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19240"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0350.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0365","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0365.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0744","title":"Netscape Enterprise Server 远程缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Netscape Enterprise Server 及 FastTrack Server 存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向目标服务器发送特制的超长 HTTP GET 请求（超过 4080 字符）触发该漏洞，导致服务进程崩溃，并可进一步在目标系统上以服务进程权限执行任意代码。该漏洞影响 Netscape Enterprise Server 3.6 SP2/4.0 及 FastTrack Server 2.0.1 等版本。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0744"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-01-04","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"升级至 Netscape Enterprise Server 4.1 或更高版本（该漏洞已在后续版本修复）。由于该产品已停止维护，建议迁移至 Oracle iPlanet Web Server 7.0+ 或 Apache httpd 等现代 Web 服务器，并在网络层限制 HTTP 请求 URI 长度以防止缓冲区溢出攻击。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/603","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19783"],"poc_urls":["https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19783"],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0365.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0365.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0365.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0756","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0756.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0964","title":"FreeBSD libc setlocale 缓冲区溢出代码执行漏洞","description":"FreeBSD libc 模块中的 setlocale 函数存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地攻击者可通过设置超长 PATH_LOCALE 环境变量触发该漏洞，导致任意代码执行。该漏洞影响多个 FreeBSD 版本，攻击者需拥有本地访问权限，成功利用后可获得目标系统的 root 权限或劫持进程控制流。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0964"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:25.217","remediation":"升级至 FreeBSD 4.0 及以上版本（该版本已修复 libc 中 PATH_LOCALE 长度检查缺失问题）；现代系统应升级至最新的受支持 FreeBSD 稳定版（如 13.x 或 14.x）。如无法升级，可通过在系统级脚本中过滤并截断 PATH_LOCALE 环境变量长度（限制 ≤256 字节）作为临缓解措施，并严格限制本地 shell 访问权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/6086"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0756.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1900","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1900.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1324","title":"OpenVMS VAXstations 登录失败锁定机制绕过漏洞","description":"Open VMS VAXstations 5.3 至 5.5-2 版本中，当使用 VMS DECwindows 或 MOTIF 图形界面时，系统未能正确限制超过登录失败阈值的用户账户访问权限。具体而言，当用户账户因多次登录失败触发 break-in 限制后，系统并未实际禁用该账户，导致攻击者可以绕过账户锁定机制持续进行暴力破解密码攻击。该漏洞降低了暴力破解的难度，使远程攻击者更容易通过枚举方式获取系统访问权限，影响所有运行受影响版本 Open VMS 的 VAXstations 设备。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":9.8,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1324"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:11.863","remediation":"升级 Open VMS 至 5.5-3 或更高版本，该版本已修复登录失败阈值检测失效问题。如无法升级，在 SYLOGIN.COM 或系统登录脚本中增加登录失败计数检查逻辑，并启用 SYSGEN 参数 LGI_BRK_LIM 强制限制。同时配置 INTRUSION_RECORD 启用入侵检测记录，监控异常登录行为。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://ciac.llnl.gov/ciac/bulletins/d-06.shtml","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/7225","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/8600ac0c091970175de0b53d9682f50858aef8dc/1999/CVE-1999-1324.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d92a0abc5d3abac6dcdfabfef6fd71c158e0fd8b/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1324.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1324","https://github.com/bb1nfosec/Information-Security-Tasks/blob/14e2094f7bd96d2cb82493a9a6968ae7aa4fed5e/feeds/2026-06-07.md","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1324.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-1324.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-5r36-3w36-p2fp/GHSA-5r36-3w36-p2fp.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cwe_details/cwe_details_200_300.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87872/info.html","https://github.com/jmohitz/SECAI/blob/33119e592f944e313664a5f75ae76284ea4b3fe8/data/CWE/307.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1900.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1888","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1888.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1293","title":"Apache HTTP Server 1.2.5 mod_proxy 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Apache HTTP Server 1.2.5 及更早版本中的 mod_proxy 模块存在拒绝服务漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向目标服务器发送特制的畸形 FTP 命令，触发 mod_proxy 模块在处理 FTP 代理请求时出现错误，导致 Apache 进程崩溃转储核心。该漏洞无需身份认证即可远程利用，影响运行 Apache 1.2.5 及之前版本的系统，攻击者可通过持续发送恶意请求造成服务不可用。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1293"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:07.733","remediation":"升级至 Apache HTTP Server 1.3.x 或更高版本（1.2.5 及更早版本已停止维护）。如无法升级，在配置中禁用 mod_proxy 模块或限制代理请求来源 IP。同时建议迁移至当前主流版本（2.4.x）以获得持续安全支持。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=88413292830649&w=2","http://www.apache.org/info/security_bulletin_1.2.5.html","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d92a0abc5d3abac6dcdfabfef6fd71c158e0fd8b/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1293.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1293","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1293.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/58eef6eedd760f280b47bfb4c94db9995b29c5a0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1293.json","https://github.com/zmerry/z-marvel.github.io/blob/581a79f0e7ceb8cdb3e444922154e004cca44bbb/vulbox/webvul/high/Apache%E7%9A%84mod_proxy%E6%8B%92%E7%BB%9D%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E(CVE-1999-1293).html","https://github.com/marcellodesales/aibbp-reverse-engineer/blob/960f610d597aae9fec1cc5f03c68679be00c222d/reverse_engineer/acunetix/vulnerabilities/vdb/1999/1xxx/cve-1999-1293.yaml","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/bc3b224aa865bb4a5c31d7720dca83e446e475e2/1999/CVE-1999-1293.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1888.toml"}]